irections →"}]]}]]}],["$","$L11",null,{"items":[{"question":"How do I book an appointment with Dr Arjun?","answer":"You can book by calling +91-9123456789, messaging on WhatsApp, or using the online booking form. Walk-ins are welcome during clinic hours."},{"question":"What should I bring to my first neurology consultation?","answer":"Please bring any previous MRI or CT scan reports, EEG reports, a list of current medications, and your insurance card if applicable."},{"question":"Do you accept insurance for neurology treatment?","answer":"Yes, we work with all major insurance providers and TPA networks. Cashless facility is available. Our team assists with pre-authorisation and claim follow-up."},{"question":"How long does recovery take after a neurological procedure?","answer":"Recovery varies depending on the condition and procedure. Dr Arjun will provide a personalised aftercare plan with a realistic timeline at your consultation."},{"question":"Is EMI available for treatment packages?","answer":"Yes, we offer zero-cost and low-cost EMI options through multiple bank partners. The approval process is quick and our team handles the paperwork."},{"question":"What are the clinic hours and location?","answer":"We are open Monday to Saturday, 9:00 AM - 7:00 PM. Located at Plot 45, Kondapur Main Road, Kondapur, Hyderabad -- easily accessible from Gachibowli, Miyapur, and Madhapur."}]}],["$","$L12",null,{"posts":[{"href":"/blog/early-signs-of-migraine","gradStyle":"background: linear-gradient(145deg,var(--secondary-deep),var(--secondary))","date":"15 Jan 2025","title":"10 Early Signs of Migraine You Should Not Ignore","excerpt":"Recognising migraine warning signs early can prevent full attacks and reduce long-term impact on daily life."},{"href":"/blog/causes-of-epilepsy","gradStyle":"background: linear-gradient(145deg,var(--secondary),var(--primary))","date":"02 Feb 2025","title":"What Causes Epilepsy and How It Is Treated","excerpt":"A clear explanation of epilepsy tri